WEBVTT

00:01:28.037 --> 00:01:30.616
"I don't give a damn about human rights.

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:33.491
I don't give a damn about the revolution.

00:01:33.515 --> 00:01:36.971
I don't give a damn
about democracy and liberty.

00:01:37.587 --> 00:01:39.177
I just want to be safe."

00:01:41.672 --> 00:01:44.014
"Satisfied?" asked his jailer.

00:01:44.896 --> 00:01:46.205
"You're safe now."

00:01:46.941 --> 00:01:49.696
If the Tunisian people can figure out

00:01:49.720 --> 00:01:51.783
how to deal with their terrorism problem

00:01:51.807 --> 00:01:54.229
without ending up in this place,

00:01:54.771 --> 00:01:57.454
they will be a model
not only for their region,

00:01:57.478 --> 00:01:58.846
but for all of us.